				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Perhaps I've just missed any discussions lately, but has there been any response other than "we're looking into this" to the a**tasticness of our pet heals when compared to Beastlords/Necros ?
<br />

<br />
Healing of Sorsha is 2100hp in 11.25 seconds, which works out to  186.66hp/second and 4.94hp/manapoint
<br />
Planar Renewal is 1200hp in 14.5 seconds or 82.76hp/second and 4hp/manapoint
<br />

<br />
I'm all for the new ginormous pets, and in fact, they could be even pimper, but shouldn't we be screaming about this still?
<br />

<br />
d<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=559842" target="_blank" class="postlink">Dagard Ben`Shachar</a>
<br />
GrumpyMage of Tunare</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
